org.pepstock.charba.client.configuration

Class ConfigurationContainer<T extends NativeObjectContainer>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pepstock.charba.client.configuration.ChartContainer
      • org.pepstock.charba.client.configuration.ConfigurationContainer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of options
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Axis, ConfigurationOptions

    abstract class ConfigurationContainer<T extends NativeObjectContainer>
extends ChartContainer
    Extends a JavaScript object container for all entities which need the options instance to store the configuration of chart.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
